text.tspan: Technical Knowledge: When he was working
he knew quite lots of technical things but
now it is hard to even use a telephone.
He likes to have a walk around the city. Since he broke the contact
with his sons he is really alone. But he got used to it. Watching
other people enjoy the life is maybe his most frequent activity.
Sometimes he think about the old nice days when he was able to
have a good time with friends and family. He is now a grumpy men.
